com.interpss.simu.multicase.aclf
Interface ContingencyAnalysis

All Superinterfaces:
AclfMultiStudyCase, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, MultiStudyCase, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
ContingencyAnalysisImpl
public interface ContingencyAnalysis
extends AclfMultiStudyCase

A representation of the model object 'Contingency Analysis'. Class for defining contingency analysis. It contains multiple contingency cases.

The following features are supported:

  • Limit Run Case
  • Max Run Case
  • Use Default Branch Mva Rating
  • Default Branch Mva Rating

See Also:
MCaseAclfPackage.getContingencyAnalysis()
